content.body:
so IIUC:
```js
asyncVar.set("foo");

await (async () => {
	asyncVar.set("bar");
})();

console.log(asyncVar.get());  // bar
```
but
```js
asyncVar.set("foo");

// No await!
(async () => {
	asyncVar.set("bar");
})();

console.log(asyncVar.get());  // foo
```
